      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\agentsong\\training\\opencode_example_unsloth.jsonl</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\"conversations\": [{\"from\": \"human\", \"value\": \"Create a simple Python function that calculates the factorial of a number\"}, {\"from\": \"gpt\", \"value\": \"[Used write]\\n```json\\ndef factorial(n):\\n    if n < 0:\\n        raise ValueError('Factorial is not defined for negative numbers')\\n    if n == 0 or n == 1:\\n        return 1\\n    result = 1\\n    for i in range(2, n + 1):\\n        result *= i\\n    return result\\n```\\nOutput:\\n```\\nFile written to factorial.py\\n```\"}], \"source\": \"agentsong\", \"session_id\": \"example-opencode-session\", \"tool\": \"opencode\", \"agent\": \"mimo-v2.5-free\"}\n\n(End of file - total 1 lines)\n</content>",
