      "type": "answer",
      "text": "Here is the full, thorough report on the current state of the `agentsong` repository at `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Documents\\agentsong`.\n\n---\n\n## AGENTSON REPO -- FULL STATE REPORT\n\n**Date:** Sunday, July 5, 2026\n\n---\n\n### 1. GIT STATUS\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **Branch** | `master` (only branch) |\n| **Remote** | `origin` -> `https://github.com/andiekobbietks/AgentSON.git` |\n| **Remote tracking** | `origin/master` (up to date) |\n| **Working tree** | CLEAN -- nothing to commit, no uncommitted changes |\n| **Stashes** | None |\n| **Tags** | None |\n| **Total branches** | 1 local (`master`) + 1 remote (`origin/master`) |\n\n---\n\n### 2. COMMIT HISTORY (8 commits total, all from today)\n\n| # | Hash | Date (UTC+0100) | Message |\n|---|------|-----------------|---------|\n| 1 | `574cb93` | Jul 5 01:55 | **Add fine-tuning exporters, ChatGPT importer, search CLI, and PWA viewer** (HEAD, latest) |\n| 2 | `33b90f1` | Jul 5 01:52 | Update README with Chrome DevTools status, add tests, fix directory structure |\n| 3 | `f8f1e54` | Jul 5 01:26 | Clarify empirical evidence vs inference for Chrome DevTools AI storage |\n| 4 | `484f0d2` | Jul 5 01:23 | Add why Preferences JSON was chosen for Chrome DevTools AI storage |\n| 5 | `4d1d311` | Jul 5 01:18 | Update SOPs index with Chrome DevTools AI mechanism |\n| 6 | `9efdc59` | Jul 5 01:17 | Add detailed Chrome DevTools AI mechanism documentation |\n| 7 | `6476e32` | Jul 5 01:12 | Add SOPs index page for better navigation |\n| 8 | `a628c1f` | Jul 5 01:09 | **Initial commit: AgentSON - Agent + JSON session capture format with 14 SOPs** |\n\nAll 8 commits were made within ~46 minutes on July 5, 2026. No commits from before today. No tags have been created.\n\n---\n\n### 3. WHAT EXISTS -- COMPLETE FILE INVENTORY\n\n**56 tracked files** across **15 top-level directories**. Total files on disk (including `__pycache__`): 66.\n\n#### 3.1 Top-Level Directories\n\n| Directory | Status | Contents |\n|-----------|--------|----------|\n| `cli/` | Implemented | `main.py` (22KB, 144+ lines changed in latest commit), `supabase_client.py` |\n| `readers/` | Implemented | `opencode.py`, `minimax.py`, `antigravity.py`, `libre.py` |\n| `exporters/` | Implemented | `__init__.py`, `finetune.py` (Unsloth + Olive training export) |\n| `importers/` | Implemented | `__init__.py`, `chatgpt.py` (ChatGPT conversations.json converter) |\n| `tests/` | Implemented | `test_opencode.py`, `test_minimax.py`, `test_antigravity.py` |\n| `examples/` | Implemented | 3 `.AgentSON` example files |\n| `training/` | Implemented | `opencode_example_unsloth.jsonl` (1 line, training data example) |\n| `spec/` | Implemented | `v1.json` (JSON Schema, 213 lines) |\n| `supabase/` | Implemented | `schema.sql` (158 lines, full DB schema with RLS) |\n| `SOPs/` | Implemented | 14 SOP markdown files (SOP-001 through SOP-014) |\n| `docs/` | Implemented | `index.html`, `sops/` (14 SOPs + Chrome DevTools doc + index), `viewer/` (index.html) |\n| `viewers/` | Implemented | `web/index.html` (drag-and-drop viewer) |\n| `pwa/` | Implemented | `index.html` (13KB), `manifest.json`, `sw.js` (PWA viewer) |\n| `normalizer/` | **EMPTY** | No files -- placeholder directory, planned but not built |\n| `renderers/` | **EMPTY** | No files -- placeholder directory, planned but not built |\n\n#### 3.2 Python Files (13 total)\n\n| File | Path | Purpose |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `main.py` | `cli/` | CLI entry point (list, export, search, render, push, pull commands) |\n| `supabase_client.py` | `cli/` | Supabase API client for push/pull |\n| `opencode.py` | `readers/` | opencode SQLite reader |\n| `minimax.py` | `readers/` | MiniMax SQLite reader |\n| `antigravity.py` | `readers/` | Antigravity IDE SQLite reader |\n| `libre.py` | `readers/` | FreeStyle Libre 2 sensor reader |\n| `finetune.py` | `exporters/` | Training data export (Unsloth/ShareGPT + Olive formats) |\n| `chatgpt.py` | `importers/` | ChatGPT conversations.json importer |\n| `__init__.py` | `exporters/` | Package init |\n| `__init__.py` | `importers/` | Package init |\n| `test_opencode.py` | `tests/` | opencode reader tests |\n| `test_minimax.py` | `tests/` | MiniMax reader tests |\n| `test_antigravity.py` | `tests/` | Antigravity reader tests |\n\n#### 3.3 Web/HTML Files (5 total)\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `pwa/index.html` | PWA viewer (13KB, standalone viewer app) |\n| `pwa/manifest.json` | PWA manifest |\n| `pwa/sw.js` | Service worker for offline caching |\n| `docs/index.html` | Documentation index page (13KB) |\n| `docs/sops/index.html` | SOPs navigation page |\n| `docs/viewer/index.html` | Docs-hosted viewer |\n| `viewers/web/index.html` | Drag-and-drop web viewer (9.8KB) |\n\n#### 3.4 Documentation Files (33 Markdown files)\n\n| File | Size | Content |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `README.md` | 9.6KB | Full project overview, quick start, schema, architecture |\n| `PRD.md` | 26KB | Complete product requirements document (718 lines) |\n| `PERSONAS-AND-USER-STORIES.md` | 10.6KB | User personas and stories |\n| `CHROME-DEVTOOLS-AI-MECHANISM.md` | 20.6KB | Chrome DevTools AI storage analysis |\n| `SOP-001` through `SOP-014` | Various | 14 Standard Operating Procedures (duplicated in `SOPs/` and `docs/sops/`) |\n\n#### 3.5 Data/Config Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `spec/v1.json` | AgentSON JSON Schema v1 (213 lines) |\n| `supabase/schema.sql` | Supabase database schema (158 lines, with RLS + search functions) |\n| `training/opencode_example_unsloth.jsonl` | Example Unsloth training data (1 line) |\n| `.gitignore` | Ignores `__pycache__/`, `.pyc`, `venv/`, `.env`, `.csv`, `.db`, `.AgentSON`, `training/` |\n\n---\n\n### 4. WHAT HAS BEEN COMMITTED\n\nEverything is committed. All 56 tracked files are part of the latest commit (`574cb93`). The working tree is completely clean -- no uncommitted changes, no staged files, no stashes.\n\n**What was in the latest commit (commit #8):**\n- `.gitignore` update (binary change, 180 -> 202 bytes)\n- `cli/main.py` (144 lines of changes -- search CLI added)\n- `exporters/__init__.py` (new)\n- `exporters/finetune.py` (237 lines, entirely new)\n- `importers/__init__.py` (new)\n- `importers/chatgpt.py` (249 lines, entirely new)\n- `pwa/index.html` (413 lines, entirely new)\n- `pwa/manifest.json` (21 lines, entirely new)\n- `pwa/sw.js` (20 lines, entirely new)\n- `training/opencode_example_unsloth.jsonl` (1 line, entirely new)\n\n**Total additions in last commit:** 1,086 lines across 10 files.\n\n---\n\n### 5. WHAT IS PENDING / NOT YET BUILT\n\nBased on the PRD, README, and directory structure:\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| `normalizer/` | **Empty placeholder** | Directory exists but contains zero files |\n| `renderers/` | **Empty placeholder** | Directory exists but contains zero files |\n| Cursor reader | **Planned** | Listed in PRD as P1, not implemented |\n| Claude Code reader | **Planned** | Listed in PRD as P1, not implemented |\n| Chrome DevTools reader | **Experimental** | JS snippet only, storage mechanism unclear |\n| VSCode extension | **Planned** | PRD section 6.2, no `vscode-extension/` directory exists |\n| `agentsong hydrate` | **Planned** | PRD section 6.2 |\n| `agentsong diff` | **Planned** | PRD section 6.3 |\n| `agentsong replay` | **Planned** | PRD section 6.3 |\n| Team sync / cloud | **Planned** | PRD section 6.3 |\n| Analytics dashboard | **Planned** | PRD section 6.3 |\n| PyPI package | **Not packaged** | No `setup.py`, `pyproject.toml`, or `requirements.txt` found |\n| npm package (PWA) | **Not packaged** | No `package.json` or `node_modules` found |\n| Supabase deployment | **Schema only** | `schema.sql` exists but no live deployment or edge functions |\n\n---\n\n### 6. EXPORTED / PACKAGED / DOWNLOADABLE OUTPUTS\n\n**No zip files, tarballs, wheel files, egg-info, dist folders, or build artifacts were found.**\n\n| Artifact Type | Found? |\n|---------------|--------|\n| `.zip` files | **NO** |\n| `.tar.gz` / `.tar.bz2` | **NO** |\n| `.whl` (Python wheel) | **NO** |\n| `.egg-info` | **NO** |\n| `dist/` directory | **NO** |\n| `build/` directory | **NO** |\n| `node_modules/` | **NO** |\n| `venv/` or `env/` | **NO** |\n| `package.json` | **NO** |\n| `requirements.txt` | **NO** |\n| `setup.py` or `pyproject.toml` | **NO** |\n| Any downloadable outputs | **NO** |\n\nThe only \"export\" artifact is the training data file `training/opencode_example_unsloth.jsonl` (1 line of JSONL, 1 example conversation), but this is source data, not a packaged output.\n\n---\n\n### 7. PYTHON CACHE FILES (not tracked, but present on disk)\n\nThese `__pycache__` directories exist on disk (excluded from git by `.gitignore`):\n\n| Path |\n|------|\n| `cli/__pycache__/main.cpython-312.pyc` (23.7KB) |\n| `readers/__pycache__/libre.cpython-312.pyc` |\n| `readers/__pycache__/antigravity.cpython-312.pyc` |\n| `readers/__pycache__/minimax.cpython-312.pyc` |\n| `readers/__pycache__/opencode.cpython-312.pyc` |\n| `exporters/__pycache__/finetune.cpython-312.pyc` |\n| `exporters/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-312.pyc` |\n\nThis indicates Python 3.12 was used, and the code has been executed/imported locally.\n\n---\n\n### 8. GITIGNORE ANALYSIS\n\nThe `.gitignore` excludes:\n- `__pycache__/`, `*.pyc` -- Python bytecode\n- `.vscode/`, `.idea/` -- IDE configs\n- `.DS_Store`, `Thumbs.db` -- OS junk\n- `*.csv`, `*.db` -- Data files (protects against accidentally committing databases)\n- `*.AgentSON` -- Session files (protects against committing exported sessions)\n- `.env`, `*.key` -- Secrets\n- `training/` -- Training data directory (note: this appears to be gitignored, but the training JSONL file was committed before the gitignore was updated)\n\n---\n\n### 9. SUMMARY\n\n**What it is:** AgentSON is a vendor-neutral session capture format and toolkit for AI coding agent sessions. It reads SQLite databases from opencode, MiniMax, and Antigravity IDE, normalizes them to a common JSON format, and provides CLI + web viewer tools.\n\n**Current state:** The project is in early MVP stage with 8 commits from a single day (July 5, 2026). The core readers, CLI, tests, schema, Supabase schema, web viewer, PWA viewer, exporters (Unsloth + Olive), and ChatGPT importer are implemented. The normalizer and renderers directories are empty placeholders. No packaging, distribution, or build artifacts exist. The repo is fully committed with a clean working tree. Nothing has been published to PyPI, no zip/tar/wheel packages were created, and no downloadable outputs exist.",
